@Hixie : any preference for naming of this API?

This message needs to be on a separate channel because it has to be intercepted by the engine (versus the `flutter/system` channel which is forwarded to the embedder).

This particular parameter is specific to the implementation of Skia - if the engine switched to another graphics library then developers' code would need to be updated.

